data.title: Palo Alto Reports
data.meta_description: Palo Alto Reports - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document outlines the security reporting standard operating procedures for SecurView System Pvt ltd. It describes the different types of predefined and custom reports that are available, including application reports, SaaS application usage reports, traffic reports, URL filtering reports, user or group activity reports, botnet reports, and PDF summary reports. Instructions are provided on how to generate, view, schedule, and export these various reports from the firewall interface. The document also covers disabling predefined reports and managing reporting storage limits.
